cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with speech emotion recognition. It also involves the use of machine learning models, specifically convolutional neural networks, which suggests it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of input features and signal length, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
